Class GameBoard

  • java.lang.Object
    • GameBoard
  • public class GameBoard
extends Object
    This is the controller to control the game flow Initializes the chess to the array list. Implements Serializable. Involved in MVC design pattern Act as "Controller" of MVC design pattern
